install pip in terminal : sudo apt-get install python python-pip curl unzip -y
                                               sudo pip install selenium
                                               sudo python3.8 -m pip install selenium <- to prevent the error that selenium did't install at 3.8Python folder
                                               // please do check the link : https://christopher.su/2015/selenium-chromedriver-ubuntu/ ,whcih have detail SOP about run selenium with python at  unbuntu OS.
                                               
install pip in vscode terminal  :  $python -m pip install selenium
                                                                 $pip show selenium
                                                                 
                                                                 
                                                                 $ sudo mv ./chromedriver /usr/local/bin/
                                                                 $ sudo chmod a+x /usr/local/bin/chromedriver
                                                                 $ chromedriver 
                                                                 //Starting ChromeDriver 2.24.417424 (c5c5ea873213ee72e3d0929b47482681555340c3) on port 9515
                                                                 //Only local connections are allowed.
                                                                 //提示 Starting ChromeDriver xxx on port 9515 信息时，说明 ChromeDriver 设置成功
